  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/edf797505d2ed6dfbbc47e06596c3a01.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=74 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Check out the latest version with numerous bug fixes and improvements!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*You can progress faster by playing it as a Clicker, or take it slow by playing Idle while doing other things. The game was designed to be relaxing</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Disclaimer</strong>: Incremental Town RPG was an experimental blend of idle and town management mechanics. While it may not be a perfect fit for all idle game fans, it remains a unique experience for players who enjoy both styles. Future projects will focus on a more refined idle gameplay approach based on community feedback.<br><br>Incremental Town RPG lets you build and manage a thriving village. Master resource management, develop a robust economy, and enjoy a relaxing experience as you equip your settlement to conquer new lands and challenges!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build, Expand, Conquer: Your Town Awaits in Incremental Town RPG</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/af462dcd21b307c4fb33344cd8b97a18.poster.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/af462dcd21b307c4fb33344cd8b97a18.webm?t=1761325689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/af462dcd21b307c4fb33344cd8b97a18.mp4?t=1761325689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/4adbf542c707141c1b40ec56bf59f00a.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=74 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ A Relaxing Base Building RPG with engaging resource management and hours of entertainment. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏝️ Beautiful Pixel Graphics and a soothing ambiance for a calming gameplay experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙️ Enjoy a satisfying progression system with strategic depth. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 Prestige Tree - Reset progress to gain permanent boosts, accelerating future growth and gameplay. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦊 Efficiently manage your team to optimize resource delivery and economic development. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔨 Forge equipment to strengthen your village and overcome new challenges. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📦 Strategically plan your resource gathering to meet various demands and improve efficiency. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛏️ Discover and utilize a wide range of items to enhance your gameplay experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎒 Fully interactive Crafting and Inventory System for streamlined management. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 Regular game content updates through expansions, keeping the experience fresh. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 Suitable for players of all ages seeking a relaxing yet engaging experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/fbff4ad6e18700ca73904c8eea0d19a0.poster.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/fbff4ad6e18700ca73904c8eea0d19a0.webm?t=1761325689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/fbff4ad6e18700ca73904c8eea0d19a0.mp4?t=1761325689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on an epic adventure filled with battles, quests, and a lot of loot. As you progress through the levels, you'll unlock new gears, vehicles, new places and buildings, allowing you to take on even tougher challenges and defeat fearsome enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/ce56387958d31c21a9486d9dd026e8f7.poster.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/ce56387958d31c21a9486d9dd026e8f7.webm?t=1761325689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/ce56387958d31c21a9486d9dd026e8f7.mp4?t=1761325689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you so much for your visit! I'm a solo indie game developer and I am doing my best to improve the game based on the community feedback. By purchasing the game you are encoraging me to keep making games even better. Best wishes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/254ff872f03f5813580ad6ec661c66cb.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=120 /></span>Incremental Town RPG does not contain microtransactions. Enjoy the complete game experience without spending money during the game.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/edf797505d2ed6dfbbc47e06596c3a01.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=74 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Check out the latest version with numerous bug fixes and improvements!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*You can progress faster by playing it as a Clicker, or take it slow by playing Idle while doing other things. The game was designed to be relaxing</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Disclaimer</strong>: Incremental Town RPG was an experimental blend of idle and town management mechanics. While it may not be a perfect fit for all idle game fans, it remains a unique experience for players who enjoy both styles. Future projects will focus on a more refined idle gameplay approach based on community feedback.<br><br>Incremental Town RPG lets you build and manage a thriving village. Master resource management, develop a robust economy, and enjoy a relaxing experience as you equip your settlement to conquer new lands and challenges!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build, Expand, Conquer: Your Town Awaits in Incremental Town RPG</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/af462dcd21b307c4fb33344cd8b97a18.poster.avif?t=1761325689\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/af462dcd21b307c4fb33344cd8b97a18.webm?t=1761325689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895430/extras/af462dcd21b307c4fb33344cd8b97a18.mp4?t